name: RBC U.S. Dividend Covered Call ETF
longDescription: In pursuing its investment objective, The ETF invests primarily in an actively managed portfolio of U.S. companies with above-average dividend yield or with good prospects of paying or growing their dividends. The ETF will write covered call options on some of these securities depending on market volatility and other factors. The ETF seeks to provide unitholders with exposure to the performance of a diversified portfolio of highquality U.S. equity securities that are expected to provide regular income from dividends and have the potential for long term capital growth, while mitigating some downside risk through the use of covered call options.
